{"type": "article", "id": 20243, "title": "极简式的洗手池和排水孔", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-05T07:00:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 88, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110605qBu9XK4UyMAhDWNT.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tMosa 是荷兰的一家瓷砖品牌，这是他们推出的洗手池和排水孔设计。洗手池是灰色的长方体，有带方形的凹槽或者带白色的圆盆，悬空在墙壁上，左右对称，干净而极简。排水孔设计成了一个长方形的缝隙，与周围的地砖是同样轮廓，完全融入在了环境当中，也是对极简风格的呼应。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110603WaBiHnFzLSsrPKcG.jpg\" width=\"913\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.78860898\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110603hO48A3d5tZCWYzVq.jpg\" width=\"496\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.4516129\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110603cHkBynW587lYzNKs.jpg\" width=\"886\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.81264108\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110604Tncv8ajrQuzBy5Hm.jpg\" width=\"961\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74921956\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110604YaI9xzQUomRLqWE5.jpg\" width=\"530\" height=\"351\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66226415\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n"}